'From Squeak3.7beta of ''1 April 2004'' [latest update: #5967] on 17 September 2004 at 12:45:35 am'!"Change Set:		DictionaryEnhTestDate:			17 September 2004Author:			Alexandre BergelTest added to DictionaryTest related to Dictionary>>includesAssociation:"!!DictionaryTest methodsFor: 'testing' stamp: 'ab 9/17/2004 00:43'!testIncludesAssociation	"self debug: #testIncludesAssociation"	| d |	d := Dictionary new 		at: #five put: 5; 		at: #givemefive put: 5;		at: #six put: 6;		yourself.			self assert: (d includesAssociation: (d associationAt: #five)).	self assert: (d includesAssociation: (#five -> 5)).	self assert: (d includesAssociation: (#five -> 6)) not.! !